    "name": "Tavern Legends",
    "steam_appid": 3160880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/e55699adff48b1b6f35fdfcfd45897f8.avif?t=1768318894\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras_big/e55699adff48b1b6f35fdfcfd45897f8.avif?t=1768318894 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tavern Legends is a medieval tavern simulation game in first-person perspective. You start with a small tavern and can, once enough gold is earned, expand your tavern and acquire new ones. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a quaint atmospheric town from the 14th century with cozy village squares, lively streets, and hearty locals. The town is freely explorable, there is much to discover, and you even have your own home! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Work Hard</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/3ce35eed77a6d62f3cab3ae41769c79e.poster.avif?t=1768318894\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/3ce35eed77a6d62f3cab3ae41769c79e.webm?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/3ce35eed77a6d62f3cab3ae41769c79e.mp4?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone starts small. At first, you’re on your own - sweeping floors, wiping tables, pouring drinks, and filling hungry bellies. Serve quickly to earn satisfied guests and generous tips. But be careful: keep them waiting too long, and your tavern’s reputation will suffer. Serve all kinds of guests - from grumpy beggars and hardworking farmers to noble knights and wealthy nobles - build your way up become known!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Building System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/5dde6c894e407cc024e846352f3afccb.poster.avif?t=1768318894\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/5dde6c894e407cc024e846352f3afccb.webm?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/5dde6c894e407cc024e846352f3afccb.mp4?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your tavern according to your own vision. Decide where guests will sit, where the bar will be, and where cooking will take place. Keep paths short and plan your storage areas wisely to create optimal work routes. Decorate your tavern with  carpets, lighting, new games for your customers and more, as this will affect your tavern's rating. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Management</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/688d70bd146b0798e57b833597d30798.poster.avif?t=1768318894\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/688d70bd146b0798e57b833597d30798.webm?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/688d70bd146b0798e57b833597d30798.mp4?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your food, store your ingredients, and ensure a steady supply. Each tavern can be customized as you wish. Should it be a classy restaurant or a rowdy nightspot? Only you decide when, where, and what selection is available. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be a Businessman</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tired of getting your hands dirty? No problem, hire people to work for you. Whether it's a cook, waiter, or cleaner, set up workflows and manage your staff. Each one has specific strengths and weaknesses, which can only be managed through good coordination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gain Popularity</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/a545626298b477c42669f90b4fd241ad.poster.avif?t=1768318894\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/a545626298b477c42669f90b4fd241ad.webm?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/a545626298b477c42669f90b4fd241ad.mp4?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your popularity in the city to attract higher-quality guests. Not everyone is the same. Every resident has a specific rank, from beggar, common citizen, guard, to even mage. For example, a beggar has low demands but is not willing to pay as much as a noble. A noble has higher expectations and will spend more gold, but won’t appreciate if only beggars are present, which can lead to a lower rating. Be cautious with price increases, as they can bring in more income and higher-ranked guests, but might also deter the lower class from visiting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With enough influence, you’ll upgrade your tavern’s level and unlock new items and facilities! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Creative</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/fd94ed618d615a1b279519a67cc97f21.poster.avif?t=1768318894\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/fd94ed618d615a1b279519a67cc97f21.webm?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/fd94ed618d615a1b279519a67cc97f21.mp4?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your menu with meals you’ve created yourself. Choose from a variety of ingredients and refine them with spices. Quality matters here too. The higher the quality and variety of your food, the higher the rank of your guests. Each guest has specific preferences, and more variations will increase their satisfaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Weather</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/dbd0e11b0b3952bf4526253105557228.poster.avif?t=1768318894\" width=512 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/dbd0e11b0b3952bf4526253105557228.webm?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/dbd0e11b0b3952bf4526253105557228.mp4?t=1768318894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a dynamic world with stunning weather effects and a realistic day-night cycle. Whether it’s bright sunshine, gentle rain, dense fog, or a roaring thunderstorm – the weather changes seamlessly and affects not only the mood but also the gameplay. Rain will drive citizens to seek refuge in the tavern, creating more mess, which impacts the cleanliness of your establishment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160880/extras/f3b1405b81f0c2ba58b6b1fa75b6828a.avif?t=1768318894\" width=1560 height=504 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tavern Legends has a build in Twitch Integration with is available during the game in the options</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some implemented features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Viewers can visit your tavern</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get gold from bits and XP from subs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheers on follower, sub, bits and raids</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Viewers can start a poll and vote for freebeer and more</p></li></ul>",
